channel.title: Help with Client logging in
channel.description:
i dont know why but before i would go on clients and logg onto servers and it would work fine.
Now: when i logg on its really laggy and it keeps on logging me in and out for no reason, please help me??? i have all the java needed :(

item.title: Help with Client logging in
item.dc:creator: @code_god_of_rs code god of rs
item.description:

Sounds like you typed some code and screwed up your server.

Jest start all over,and next time remember every time your done with something save!
